

	 --     Step Response of a Linear System
	 --           a simple repeated-run study
	 -----------------------------------------------------------
	 display N1 |  display C8
	 TMAX=0.5 |  DT=0.0001 |  NN=1001
	 ww=400 |  u=440
	 -----------------------------------------------------------
	 for i=1 to 5 |  -- set parameter values
	   r=10*i
	   drunr  |  display 2
	   next
	 --------------------------------
	 DYNAMIC
	 --------------------------------
	 d/dt x=xdot
	 d/dt xdot=-ww*x-r*xdot+u
	 X=x-scale |  dispt X

